  "title": "Bridgehead Post Advance",
  "notes": "Eighth real slice extends east from chapter-07 into a bridge road and bridgehead post. It reuses the current gate, shop, chest, and battle patterns so the only new pressure is cross-chapter map stitching and another chapter-local reference pack. / 第八段真实切片从 chapter-07 继续向东扩展到桥头路与桥头哨所。它继续复用现有的门禁、商店、宝箱和战斗样式，因此新增压力主要集中在跨章地图拼接和章节级 reference pack 维护上。",
  "dialogueLines": [
    {
      "id": "bridge-captain-line-issue",
      "speakerName": "桥头都伯",
      "speakerNpcId": "bridge-captain",
      "text": "桥头那边已经整队完了。你先带着这道桥令去见守兵，他验过之后才会放你过去。",
      "portraitId": "guide-default",
      "soundId": "voice-guide",
      "styleId": "dialogue-default",
      "locale": "zh-CN"
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-captain-line-repeat",
      "speakerName": "桥头都伯",
      "speakerNpcId": "bridge-captain",
      "text": "桥令已经交给你了。别在桥口耽搁，桥头守兵只认令牌。",
      "portraitId": "guide-default",
      "soundId": "voice-guide",
      "styleId": "dialogue-default",
      "locale": "zh-CN"
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-sentry-line-blocked",
      "speakerName": "桥头守兵",
      "speakerNpcId": "bridge-sentry",
      "text": "没有桥令，桥头木栅不能开。前面的人马还在等军令。",
      "portraitId": "guard-default",
      "soundId": "voice-guard",
      "styleId": "dialogue-default",
      "locale": "zh-CN"
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-sentry-line-open",
      "speakerName": "桥头守兵",
      "speakerNpcId": "bridge-sentry",
      "text": "桥令无误。我这就把木栅让开，进桥头后先去粮棚补给。",
      "portraitId": "guard-default",
      "soundId": "voice-guard",
      "styleId": "dialogue-default",
      "locale": "zh-CN"
    },
    {
      "id": "bridgehead-gate-line-blocked",
      "speakerName": "系统",
      "text": "桥头守兵还没有放行，前面的木栅暂时不会打开。",
      "portraitId": "system-default",
      "soundId": "sfx-blocked",
      "styleId": "system-default",
      "locale": "zh-CN"
    },
    {
      "id": "bridgehead-gate-line-open",
      "speakerName": "系统",
      "text": "桥头木栅已经抬起，前面的补给哨所可以进入。",
      "portraitId": "system-default",
      "soundId": "sfx-gate-open",
      "styleId": "system-default",
      "locale": "zh-CN"
    },
    {
      "id": "bridgehead-shop-line",
      "speakerName": "桥头粮官",
      "speakerNpcId": "bridge-quartermaster",
      "text": "过桥的人都在这里领补给。药包和干粮都备着，缺什么就拿什么。",
      "portraitId": "merchant-default",
      "soundId": "voice-merchant",
      "styleId": "dialogue-default",
      "locale": "zh-CN"
    },
    {
      "id": "bridgehead-cache-line-open",
      "speakerName": "系统",
      "text": "你在桥头角落的补给箱里找到一份行军干粮和一卷绷带。",
      "portraitId": "system-default",
      "soundId": "sfx-chest",
      "styleId": "system-default",
      "locale": "zh-CN"
    }
  ],
